-installed laravel intervention for image control
-used repository design pattern to organize logic and separate it from controller
-made user service provider to inject user repository in any place in the project containing its interface
-made trait for file upload to upload files
-made polymorphic relationship to store file paths and its properties in database
-used model events to upload files if exists in request before storing user in the database
-used enums to facilitate code reading and database optimization that i store tiny int values in database for user types
-used form request class to validate coming values

